Bootstrap: oci
From: python:3.11-slim

%labels
    Author apptainer_poc
    Description Python 3.11 with Dask for distributed HPC workloads

%post
    pip install --no-cache-dir "dask[complete]" numpy

%runscript
    exec python3 "$@"

%help
    Python 3.11 container with Dask for parallel/distributed computing.

    Usage:
        apptainer run dask.sif script.py
        apptainer exec dask.sif python3 -c "import dask; print(dask.__version__)"
